metadata.name: Tito "The Hood Santa" Rodriguez x Snoop Dogg RIAA Certified Platinum Record - Edition #2
metadata.description: Platinum record music producer Tito “The Hood Santa” Rodriguez, turned philanthropist partners with ZUZ Protocol to offer his personal RIAA Certified Snoop Dogg Platinum record for Local Hearts Foundation.  This NFT comes with digital RIAA certified physical Snoop Dogg Presents: Tha Eastsidaz platinum plaque.  This digital plaque NFT can also be used as a staking booster to Lightning - ZUZ Protocol’s staking platform to get even more rewards.
